    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some expected signs of its journey so far, it still offers a solid driving experience and plenty of character. It's the perfect opportunity to get behind the wheel of a dependable car at a great value!",
