    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine currently runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks from the undercarriage. The exterior has extensive rust, several deep dents, and the paint is heavily oxidized, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or a source for parts, but it is not currently in road-ready condition.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it were brand new. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with no scratches, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather and trim showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-quality vehicle that looks and drives like it just left the factory.",
